tip.text: $6.90 for a large cafe mocha, no coffee art, coffee is so-so only. The cafe is very dark, if you sit under the spotlight it is very hot. The aircon is also not sufficient.
Too pricey for this quality of food! The matcha latte with softie is super overpriced at $8.80++ and half the cup is ice cubes?! Ice water costs $0.50++??? Don't think it's worth a 2nd visit at all.
